<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318505>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Maechidius echinoides Prokofiev, new species. (A) dorsal view, holotype; (B) protibia, holotype; (C) aedeagus, lateral view, holotype; (D) parameres, dorsal view, holotype; (E) spiculum gastrale, lateral view, holotype; (F) ditto, dorsal view; (G) protibia, female paratype. Scale bars: (A) 1.5 mm; (B, G) 1.0 mm; (C–F) 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318505/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318511>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Holotype of Maechidius macrosoma Prokofiev, new species. (A) dorsal view; (B) protibia; (C) hind tarsi, lateral view; (D) aedeagus, lateral view; (E) parameres, dorsal view; (F) spiculum gastrale, dorsal view; (G) ditto, dorsolateral view. Scale bars: (A) 2.0 mm; (B, D–G) 1.0 mm; (C) 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318511/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318513>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Maechidius hirtipes Arrow, 1941, lectotype (A) and M. subcostatus Heller, 1895, lectotype (B), dorsal view. Not in scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318513/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318517>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Holotype of Maechidius penicilliger Prokofiev, new species. (A) dorsal view; (B) first three abdominal ventrites, ventral view (medial protuberances arrowed); (C) protibia; (D) hind tarsi, lateral view; (E) aedeagus, lateral view; (F) parameres, dorsal view; (G) spiculum gastrale, dorsal view; (H) ditto, lateral view. Scale bars: (A, C, D) 1.0 mm; (B, E–H) 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318517/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318499>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Holotype of Maechidius bombycinus Prokofiev, new species. (A) dorsal view; (B) protibia; (C) aedeagus, lateral view; (D) parameres, dorsal view; (E) spiculum gastrale, dorsal view; (F) ditto, lateral view. Scale bars: (A, B) 1.0 mm; (C–F) 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318499/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318523>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Holotype of Maechidius telnovi Prokofiev, new species. (A) dorsal view; (B) lateral view; (C) protibia; (D) aedeagus, lateral view; (E) parameres, dorsal view; (F) spiculum gastrale, dorsal view. Scale bars: (A–C) 1.0 mm; (D–F) 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318523/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318528>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Male syntype of Maechidius muticus Arrow, 1941. (A) dorsal view; (B) lateral view; (C) protibia. Not in scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318528/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

